#: ../../source/api_reference/dsp.rst:672
#: 58e5b3e29e46462ba424ba80f18ca21b
msgid "**滤波器效果，用于按截止频率、斜率、增益和共振塑造频率响应。**"
msgstr "**Filter effect for shaping frequency response with cutoff frequency, slope, gain, and resonance.**"

#: ../../source/api_reference/dsp.rst:677
#: bdfc546b807647dea454909446b1a2e4
msgid ""
"**FmodAudioEffectFilter** 提供基础滤波控制，可通过 ``cutoff_hz`` 设置截止频率，通过 ``db`` 选择截止曲线斜率，并用 ``gain`` 与 ``resonance`` 调整滤波后的信号强度和共振感。它适合制作低通、高通、遮挡、远近感或菜单过渡等效果。"
msgstr ""
"**FmodAudioEffectFilter** provides basic filtering controls. Use ``cutoff_hz`` to set the cutoff frequency, ``db`` to choose the cutoff slope, and ``gain`` plus ``resonance`` to adjust the filtered signal level and resonance. It is suitable for low-pass, high-pass, occlusion, distance, and menu transition effects."

